{"tid":186730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩夢想的香港人最慘?","createTime":"2017-04-04T12:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T12:12:09.000Z","uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82d3379c1b24dd9e3f7c1b6565f050cc06d0d7dd","tid":186730,"uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"想做外交官果班人<br />\n<br />\n唔係香港駐外經貿處果d, 係真係做人地外交官工作果種<br />\n佢地就算移左民都做唔到, 好多國家第一代移民都做唔到外交官<br />\n姐係佢地一世都完成唔到夢想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到仲有想做太空或軍事科技的都慘, 但這些行業多商業化, 有能力都有機會入到行<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他夢想好慘?<br />\n(有置業夢唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"bda12760d742ca49cb355cbedf28d0071ff1817b","tid":186730,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffa4adc27b113c7ff5a795c0d488c78ef658ce7","tid":186730,"uid":80499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係"}]}